<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: white; padding: 30px; border: 2px solid #f59e0b; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .info-box { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .safe-box { background: #d1fae5; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .code { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 10px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; }
    h2 { color: #92400e; margin-top: 0; }
    ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;"><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.heading') %></h1>
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">
      <%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.intro', token: @migration.token) %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="safe-box">
      <h2 style="color: #065f46; margin-top: 0;">Your Account is Safe</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 0;">
        The PLC directory was <strong>not modified</strong>. Your account remains on
        <strong><%= @migration.old_pds_host %></strong> and all your migration data
        (repository, blobs, preferences) is safely stored and ready.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h2 style="color: #92400e; margin-top: 0;">What Happened?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;">
        The confirmation code from your old PDS provider expired before it could be used.
        These codes are only valid for a limited time (typically 1 hour).
      </p>
      <% if @error_message.present? %>
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 0;">
        <strong><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.error_detail', error: @error_message) %></strong>
      </p>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #dbeafe; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
      <h2 style="color: #1e40af; margin-top: 0;"><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.what_to_do') %></h2>
      <ol style="font-size: 15px; color: #1e3a8a;">
        <li><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.step1') %></li>
        <li><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.step2') %></li>
        <li><%= t('mailers.plc_token_failed.step3') %></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="<%= @migration_url %>" class="button">
        Go to Migration Status Page
      </a>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #fef9c3; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #eab308;">
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #854d0e; margin: 0;">
        <strong>Migration Details:</strong><br>
        Token: <%= @migration.token %><br>
        DID: <%= @migration.did %><br>
        Old PDS: <%= @migration.old_pds_host %><br>
        New PDS: <%= @migration.new_pds_host %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated notification from <%= EuroskyConfig::SITE_NAME %></p>
    <p>Migration Token: <%= @migration.token %></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
